message.body: Hey there! Sorry to call you so last minute! I hope I didn't add any stress or anything and like I said we are here til tomorrow so if brunch or something is easier let me know! And if you're headed downtown tell me where we can meet you
Do we just take the 96 bus across town?
Actually, can I meet you on the east side in like an hour and 20?
Do you want to make plans now or do you want to call when you're heading over?
I'm on 89th and 1st. I don't know what to do around here but I'm cool with whatever.
I can probably leave here around 9.
Okay. We are coming from 3rd and 95th. We can ask her cousin! She is getting home from work at 9 so we will hand off the apt key and ask her
Also do you care if her cousin comes?
I'll be leaving here in like 5-10 minutes. Sorry it keeps changing.

No worries! We are sitting in her apt talking. The place she recommended is a tavern we can sit and talk, you and I can get a drink if you want (sorry I changed my mind haha it's fine if you want to do that) and we can sit and talk :) it's kinsale tavern on 3rd between 93rd and 94th
K I'll meet you there in a few.
Are you leaving now? Should we head over?
